  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>What is DEAD and what do I do?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is designed as a classic arcade shooter game. You can play with up to 4 people locally, or using Steam Remote play. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your goal is to clear out as many enemies as you can, and earn the highest score.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Updates?</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This originally came out in 2020 as a fun, 1 month long project I developed and It has continued to be updated as of 2026. Currently I am revamping all available maps so if one was available and is not.. it will be.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please keep updated via the announcements tab in our Steam Community. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Issues?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you find any bugs, have a feature, quality of life idea, or anything else you might want/need: please write up a discussion in the community hub for the game. I see all. This is preferred over a negative review. I go out of my way to fix anything wrong with the title whenever I get the chance!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Good luck!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Last updated: (03/10/2026).  </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>What is DEAD and what do I do?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is designed as a classic arcade shooter game. You can play with up to 4 people locally, or using Steam Remote play. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your goal is to clear out as many enemies as you can, and earn the highest score.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Updates?</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This originally came out in 2020 as a fun, 1 month long project I developed and It has continued to be updated as of 2026. Currently I am revamping all available maps so if one was available and is not.. it will be.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please keep updated via the announcements tab in our Steam Community. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Issues?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you find any bugs, have a feature, quality of life idea, or anything else you might want/need: please write up a discussion in the community hub for the game. I see all. This is preferred over a negative review. I go out of my way to fix anything wrong with the title whenever I get the chance!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Good luck!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Last updated: (03/10/2026).  </p>",
